                <h1>Understanding Backstory: The Key to Meaningful Characters</h1>
                <p>Backstory refers to the history behind a character or a narrative context, explaining their motivations and life events that shaped their personality. It enriches storytelling by adding depth and emotional resonance, helping audiences understand characters’ decisions, conflicts, and relationships in a more meaningful way.</p>
